OL,3,COliver Glasner excited for 'new
OL,4,Cchapter' at Nottingham Forest
OL,6,FNottingham Forest might be on their
OL,7,Ffifth head coach in a year but so far
OL,8,FOliver Glasner is only feeling heat
OL,9,Ffrom the sun.
OL,11,FHe spoke for almost an hour in his
OL,12,Ffirst press conference. It was
OL,13,Frefreshing to hear a coach speak so
OL,14,Fopenly and show his fun side.
OL,16,FI asked if anything had surprised him
OL,17,Fsince joining the club. He said: "Oh
OL,18,Fyes, definitely, I think you can see
OL,19,Fin my face I underestimated the sun."
OL,26,@yD@bOU{D@eO]
