PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784274472
OL,3,COliver Glasner excited for 'new
OL,4,Cchapter' at Nottingham Forest
OL,6,FWith skin almost matching the red of
OL,7,Fthe press conference backboard, he
OL,8,Fwent on, "I expected cloud and
OL,9,Fprobably rain... when I came home I
OL,10,Fsaid 'oh you didn't take suncream' so
OL,11,Ftoday I took 50SPF and tomorrow it
OL,12,Fshould be better."
OL,14,FDespite his inability to check Des's
OL,15,Fweather forecasts, he is a seriously
OL,16,Fgood football manager.
OL,18,FAt Crystal Palace he won the FA Cup,
OL,19,FCommunity Shield and Europa Conference
OL,20,FLeague.
OL,26,@pD@JOUtD@RO]
