OL,3,COliver Glasner excited for 'new
OL,4,Cchapter' at Nottingham Forest
OL,6,FHe says the Forest players 'tasted
OL,7,Fhoney' with European football last
OL,8,Fseason and that will help drive them
OL,9,Fto success under him.
OL,11,FWhilst he's been impressed by the
OL,12,Fplayers so far he believes the real
OL,13,Ftest will come after the initial
OL,14,Fhoneymoon period. He likened it to his
OL,15,Fmarriage and the importance of
OL,16,F'keeping things exciting' after over
OL,17,F30 years together.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
