PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784274472
OL,3,COliver Glasner excited for 'new
OL,4,Cchapter' at Nottingham Forest
OL,6,FSome eyebrows were raised when he was
OL,7,Fappointed because of his past at
OL,8,FPalace - who have a rivalry with
OL,9,FForest after they lost a battle in the
OL,10,Fcourts over which European competition
OL,11,Fthey should enter.
OL,13,FHe said: "I had more than two
OL,14,Ffantastic years at Palace. I had an
OL,15,Famazing time there... I am really
OL,16,Fpleased having been part of this
OL,17,Fjourney but now a new chapter begins
OL,18,Ffor me, a new book is to be written
OL,19,Fand that's here at Nottingham Forest."
OL,26,@uD@JOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
