FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784274472
OL,3,COliver Glasner excited for 'new
OL,4,Cchapter' at Nottingham Forest
OL,6,FGlasner joined Forest because of the
OL,7,Fambition of the owner Evangelos
OL,8,FMarinakis. Over a dinner in Athens he
OL,9,Fsays he was shocked to meet a man who
OL,10,Fis even more ambitious than him.
OL,12,FSticking with the food theme, Glasner
OL,13,Fsays this summer is like putting the
OL,14,Fingredients together for a meal.
OL,16,FHe says it will take three to six
OL,17,Fmonths for his ideas to properly come
OL,18,Fthrough. The big question is if
OL,19,FMarinakis will have the patience to
OL,20,Flet him cook?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
